<h2 id="pagetitle">GMK Warranty Policy</h2>
<p>Your GMK product has been designed and manufactured in order to provide maximum satisfaction and safety. It is guaranteed for two years with a valid proof of purchase against any manufacturing or material defects. This guarantee does not cover damages that arise from business use, improper assembly or set up, normal wear and tear, accessories or defects that result from misuse.</p>
<h2>Conditions of Use</h2>
<p>GMK is solely intended for personal and leisure use. GMK accepts no responsibility, nor does it provide the benefits of the limited warranty, if a GMK product is used for business or commercial purposes.</p>
<p>To ensure that the product is used correctly and safely, it must be set up and used as directed in the included instructions.</p>
<h2>Limited Warranty</h2>
<p>Under the terms of this limited warranty, GMK will replace, repair, or send a replacement part free of charge if the product has been properly maintained.

